{"tid":821390,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] 美少女唐詩詠化身神醫替陳敏之急救。。。","createTime":"2018-09-16T02:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T05:25:45.000Z","uid":82917,"like":37,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2362841db0d77fd066e2d605c10213916edf661f","tid":821390,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/103411_5367dad8fb87d896321882137362b0e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F103411_5367dad8fb87d896321882137362b0e2.png&h=49418832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，陳敏之（專才）上載與好友唐詩詠（37歲）的合照，並留言因屍詠的細心善良，才令自己的腳仔及時得已治療！人美心善的屍詠除了有「絕世好女友」此美譽之外，更被封「美少女<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">37</span></span>神醫」！成為眾人榜樣。<br />\n曾扮演醫生並擁有豐富醫學常識的她，竟自行研發出用薰衣草油止血，真係唔講都無人知。小美恍然大悟，原來偶像如此多才多藝，「有身材有演技，仲有火善良的心」。。。"},{"pid":"1dd74ec1d1d06d8e1ad2177dc395cace28b7cca4","tid":821390,"uid":82917,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:45:43.000Z","msg":"小美強烈建議兩位重返校園修讀中文課程，以藝人黎講，用中文字用到出神入化，他日必成大器！！！<br />\n<br />\n例子如下：<br />\n有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">火</span>善良的心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">慢慢</span>長夜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5bebc3da3b6a30e94cbd8bfcc3a4ac27129448","tid":821390,"uid":20725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:46:20.000Z","msg":"唐姨好煩"},{"pid":"123957694140a6df51c80f2da525614101d71525","tid":821390,"uid":82917,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"1dd74ec1d1d06d8e1ad2177dc395cace28b7cca4","tid":821390,"uid":82917,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:45:43.000Z","msg":